Linkalope,API,allows,developers,to,bring,recently,shared,links,from,Twitter,into,their,own,website,or,application,Linkalope,is,a,site,that,lets,users,find,the,most,recently,shared,links,for,topics,and,people,they,follow,Users,can,access,the,Twitter,advanced,search,operators,to,refine,their,search,The,API,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON,or,RSS